# RealmJoinPhaseChanged v1 — RealmJoin DeploymentPhase transition.
# Posted by RealmJoinWatcherAdapter on every observed DeploymentPhase change (dual-emitted
# alongside the existing realmjoin_phase_changed InformationalEvent). Payload carries the
# current and previous phase DWORDs.
# Reducer: HandleRealmJoinPhaseChangedV1 → always updates RealmJoinFacts.LastDeploymentPhase
# (restart-safe persistence; fixes realmjoin_timeout reporting "last phase: 0"). When the
# phase leaves the first-deployment window (100/101) for a regular deployment phase (200/210)
# without CompletedFirstDeployment (110) ever being observed, the RJ ESP was aborted (e.g.
# interactive logon during first deployment reclassified the run as secondary-user): emits
# realmjoin_first_deployment_incomplete (Warning), cancels the RealmJoinTimeout deadline and
# releases the completion gate via CompleteIfDeferredOrBookkeep with
# Outcome="FirstDeploymentIncomplete".
